  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        The patient population consists of patients who were at risk of death from refractory,
        advanced heart failure and implanted with a HeartWare® Ventricular Assist System under IDE
        G070199.

        Patients must have participated as a study patient in a prior HeartWare trial under IDE
        G070199, and been implanted with the HeartWare® System
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. The patient has participated in a prior HeartWare trial under IDE G070199.

          2. The patient was implanted with the HeartWare® Ventricular Assist System and was an
             active patient in the prior trial.

          3. The patient has signed informed consent for participation in the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. The patient is unwilling or unable to comply with trial requirements.

          2. The patient did not sign the informed consent.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
